structure.unit: LICENSING OF MOTOR VEHICLES, OPERATORS, AND TRAILERS

law.history: Repealed 1956 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 7, Art. X, sec. 13, effective September 1, 1956. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 127, sec. 9.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Highway Patrol to take up cancelled, revoked or suspended licenses.
